The DNS Hierarchy

The last domain reference in the "Note" box should be:
   rhatcert.com.  (with a trailing dot)
rather than
   rhatcert.com

Configuring Trust Anchors

Use a DNSKEY resource record from the answer section of the dig output, not the
entire dig output.

Dumping and Changing the Unbound Cache

To flush an entire zone's records from the cache, use:
   unbound-control flush_zone <zone_name>

Review Questions

6. The answer to this question should include the word "allow" after the
network address:

forward-addr: 192.168.4.0/24 allow
